description: Converts a list of peptides into a list of kinases.
name: UKA_TT_app

model.description: Find kinase activity changes from differential peptide phosphorylation.

factors.name: Measurement
factors.description:
Select the factor that defines the values to use in the computation.

Example:
* log transform of S100
* log transformed and ComBat Corrected S100
* VSN transformed S100
* VSN transformed and ComBat Corrected S100

factors.name: Variable
factors.description:
Select the peptide identifier.

Example:
* ID

factors.name: Supergroup
factors.description:
Select a factor that identifies the Supergroup. Supergroup(s) define each comparison group for which UKA should be run. 

Example:
* Supergroup
* Replicate
* Cell line

factors.name: Group
factors.description:
Select the factor that defines the comparison groups.

Example:
* Test Condition
* Treatment off chip

factors.name: Observation
factors.description:
Select the factor(s) defining a single value per cell.

Example:
* Barcode and Row
* Barcode and Array
 * Sample Name
